headline: 3 Reasons to Sell WAT and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Waters Corporation trades at $386.11 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 10.4% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 13.4%.
